    <title>把 Airflow 搬进 Kubernetes</title>
    <link href="https://maples7.com/2019/12/03/develop-etl-via-airflow-on-k8s/"/>
    <id>https://maples7.com/2019/12/03/develop-etl-via-airflow-on-k8s/</id>
